Package: MADloy
Type: Package
Title: Package to detect individuals with LOY in SNP array and sequence data
Version: 0.9.5-25
Date: 2015-09-14
Author: Marcos Lopez-Sanchez and Juan R Gonzalez
Maintainer: Juan R Gonzalez <jrgonzalez@creal.cat>
Depends: 
    BiocStyle,
    data.table,
    R (>= 3.2.0),
Imports: 
    BiocGenerics,
    ecolitk,
    GenomeInfoDb,
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    mixtools,
    parallel,
    plotrix,
    Rsamtools,
    TEQC
Description: This packages implements a method to detect loss of Y events using
    .bam files from exome sequencing or microarray data.It compares the
    coverage in the chromosome Y, a region of interest in chrY:7000000-30000000
    and a given chromosome in UCSC format.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://www.creal.cat/brge and http://www.creal.cat/jrgonzalez/software.htm
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown
LazyData: TRUE
